-- Sumitomo Mitsui Bank to Invest in India's Kotak Mahindra, Nikkei Reports
-- Heather Burke
-- 2010-06-29T17:38:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/sumitomo-mitsui-bank-to-invest-in-india-s-kotak-mahindra-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Sumitomo Mitsui Financial Group
Inc.’s Sumitomo Mitsui Banking Corp. plans to invest almost 30
billion yen ($339.1 million) in Kotak Mahindra Bank, India’s
fourth-largest private-sector bank, Nikkei English News
reported, without saying where it got the information.  
 The investment will be the first by a Japanese bank in an
Indian one, Nikkei said.  
          
          


  


        